    - target: {fileID: 4315932971525939294, guid: e17764010848dc94fad0ede0df41355d, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: "Next, let\u2019s talk training. Once a week, you can whip your team
        into shape with a training session. It boosts their skills, but don\u2019t
        get greedy, you only get one shot per week. Pick the right focus, and your
        squad will be unstoppable. Mess it up? Well, you\u2019ve got me to bail you
        out!"
