    - target: {fileID: 4315932971525939294, guid: e17764010848dc94fad0ede0df41355d, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: "Here\u2019s where the fun gets wild! Every week, you\u2019ll pick between
        two event that we should deal with. Once you choose, boom! You have a problem
        to solve. Depending of your choice it will boost your Moral, Front Office
        Points, Fan Support Points or Equipment. Pick smart, \u2018cause these events
        are your ticket to staying on top. I\u2019d choose for you, but, y\u2019know,
        I\u2019m too busy!"
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4315932971525939294, guid: e17764010848dc94fad0ede0df41355d, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_fontSize
